We also find encouragement through his organization,

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:50.899
things we read in the literature or magazines

00:14:50.899 --> 00:14:55.600
and we greatly benefit from the congregation meetings.

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:59.799
We also benefit from sweet association with our brothers.

00:14:59.799 --> 00:15:02.600
We live or we are television,

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:07.600
so do not give up.

00:15:08.100 --> 00:15:14.100
When they shepherd also a big help for many to persevere.

00:15:14.100 --> 00:15:18.600
Publishers in our congregation do a lot to strengthen us.

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:20.600
According to Hebrews 10.25,

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:25.100
it is God's will that we keep encouraging one another

00:15:25.100 --> 00:15:30.600
and doing so is more urgent now than ever before.

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:37.100
Let us always keep in mind the inspired words of 2 Thessalonians 3.13.

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:44.100
For you apart, brothers, do not give up in doing good.

00:15:44.100 --> 00:15:47.100
Galatians 6.9 similarly says,

00:15:47.100 --> 00:15:51.100
quote, let us not give up in doing what is fine.

00:15:51.100 --> 00:15:55.440
For in due time we will reap.

00:15:55.440 --> 00:15:58.440
What do we conclude from this?

00:15:58.440 --> 00:16:03.440
It is the words of our theme text, 2 Corinthians 4.16.

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:06.440
We do not give up.
